---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Learn Vastu Basics">

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;">
  <span style="color:#0ea5e9;">Vas</span>
  <span style="color:#000;">tu Knowledge</span>
</h2>


  <div class="space-y-8">

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      1. What is Vastu?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Balancing of 5 elements in a property is Vastu.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      2. How many directions are there in Vastu?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      There are 16 directions in Vastu.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      3. What is a Vastu anomaly or defect?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      According to Vastu Shastra, each zone elementally represents certain meanings, colors, utilities, and shapes. When a zone has irrelevant colors, shapes, objects, etc., it is considered a Vastu defect. This can be corrected easily.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      4. What are the 5 elements?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Air, fire, earth, water, and space/ether define Vastu. Earth represents stability, space represents fulfillment, water represents flow, air represents communication, and fire represents fame, power, and cash flow.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      5. Ideal directions for toilet
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      SSW is ideal. ESE and WNW are also decent directions. Only the WC is considered, not the whole toilet room.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      6. Ideal directions for kitchen
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      SE is the best direction. SSE and S are also suitable as fire zones.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      7. Dangerous directions for bedroom
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      NE, SSW, WNW, and ESE are bad directions for sleeping.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      8. Can medical issues be identified through Vastu?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Yes. Each direction represents an organ; defects or anti-elements in that direction can cause health problems.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      9. Dangerous directions for kitchen
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      NW, SW, ESE, and NE are bad directions for stove placement.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      10. Positions causing divorce
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Anomalies like kitchen or toilet in SW can lead to divorce and loss of wealth.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      11. How to manifest desires using Vastu
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      At W4 (262°–269° from center): write practical desires on a circular white paper in black pen. Generally manifests in 48 days.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      12. Can industries, hospitals, schools be corrected according to Vastu?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Yes, they can.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      13. Why Vastu correction if we pray to God?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Famous temples are built according to calculations in Viswakarma Prakash. Main deities are placed in manifesting directions like W4 (e.g., Tirupati, Siddhi Vinayak, Padmanabhaswamy, Haji Ali).
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      14. Will house aesthetics be compromised after Vastu correction?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Corrections are designed so that your house does not look ugly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      15. Does wall color affect living space?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Neutral colors give fulfillment. Multi-colored walls should be analyzed to avoid anomalies in specific zones.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      16. Ideal placement for jewels and valuables
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      SW for protection. W3/W4 can multiply valuables quickly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      17. Can I get a job through Vastu?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Strengthening the North direction can attract your dream job.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      18. Loans and debt problems
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Anti-elements in NW (kitchen, toilet, windows, entry) can lead to debt. Can be corrected.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      19. Ideal direction for children to study
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      WSW. Knowledge retention is like photographic memory.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      20. Best entrances in Vastu
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      W3, W4, S3, S4, N8, E3, E4, N3, N4.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      21. Astro Vastu
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Each direction represents a zodiac. Chart helps identify favorable and unfavorable directions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      22. Numero Vastu
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Based on life and karmic numbers; strengthens specific directions for prosperity.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      23. Bad positions for wardrobes
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Air and water zones are not ideal for wardrobes.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      24. Causes of anxiety and depression
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Bedroom in ESE/WNW or spending time here; entries/windows in ESE/WNW.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      25. Legal issues through Vastu
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Anomalies in NW or SE can cause legal issues; can be corrected.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      26. Lack of opportunities
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Fire or earth element in north part causes lack of opportunities.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      27. Extra-marital affairs detection
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      NNW is the sex/attraction direction; kitchen/toilet here can cause intimacy issues.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      28. Mental health issues
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      NE is for mental clarity; anomalies here can cause issues and can be corrected.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      29. Lung problems
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Anti-elements in WSW/W, e.g., air-conditioner placement, can create lung issues.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      30. Reason for body weight gain
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Placement of cupboard in SSW or imbalance causes excessive weight gain.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      31. Wasteful expenditure
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      E2, S6, S7 entries or anomalies here can cause wasteful spending.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      32. Feeling powerless and underconfident
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      SSE is direction of power/confidence; toilet or water element here reduces confidence.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      33. Feeling unsupported
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Anomalies in NW cause loneliness and unsupported feelings.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      34. WiFi router placement and anger issues
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      Placement in SE can cause anger; remove if present.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4" style="font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive; color:#0ea5e9;">
      35. Who are Devtas and their roles?
    </h2>
    <p class="text-gray-950 font-semibold text-lg drop-shadow-md mt-2" style="font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;">
      They rule 45 energy fields of the Vastu mandal. Names: Brahma, Bhudar, Aryama, Vivaswan, Aapaha, Aapahavasta, Savita, Savitra, Indra, Jaya, Rudra, Rajyakshma, Shikhi, Prajanya, Jayant, Mahendra, Surya, Satya, Bhrisha, Antriksh, Anil, Pusha, Vitasta, Griha spatya, Yama, Gandharva, Bhriangraj, Mrigah, Pitra, Dauwarik, Sugreev, Pushpadant, Varun, Asur, Shosha, Papyakshma, Roga, Ahir, Mukhya, Bhallat, Soma, Bhujag, Aditi, Diti.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

  </section>

</Layout>
<Footer />